<gucp-dialog ref="platformDialog" :title="dialog.title" :confirm-label="dialog.labelName"
  @confirm="onConfirmCreateType('createForm')">
  <el-form ref="createForm" :model="createForm" label-width="80px" label-suffix=":" label-position="right">
    <el-form-item :label="$t('scene')" prop="scenarioName">
      <el-input v-model="createForm.scenarioName" :placeholder="$t('scene')" />
    </el-form-item>
    <el-form-item :label="$t('describe')" prop="scenarioDesc">
      <el-input v-model="createForm.scenarioDesc" :placeholder="$t('describe')" />
    </el-form-item>
    <el-form-item :label="$t('source')" prop="Platform">
      <el-select v-model="createForm.platformId" product @change="platformIdChange">
        <el-option v-for="item in platformArr" :key="item.id" :label="item.platformDesc" :value="item.id" />
      </el-select>
    </el-form-item>
    <el-form-item :label="$t('profile')" prop="Profile">
      <el-select v-model="createForm.profileId" product>
        <el-option v-for="item in profileArr" :key="item.id" :label="item.profileName" :value="item.id" />
      </el-select>
    </el-form-item>
    <el-form-item :label="$t('Point')" prop="exposurePoint">
        <el-input  v-model="createForm.exposurePoint"  :placeholder="$t('Point')"></el-input>
    </el-form-item>
  </el-form>
</gucp-dialog>
